{
  "stem": "19921.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I went in a-- on a-- not on a passenger train, just I jump on a train, and that's it.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And hoping that it was going the right direction.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It could have turned left and go to Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But fortunately for me, I suppose somebody was watching me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] I jump on the train without my suitcase.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I lost the suitcase.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I lost the suitcase.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I was on the train.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And, you know, from-- from Cracow to Bochnia would have taken about 35 minutes normal.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But that was not [LAUGHS] normal time in those days.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So we arrive.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Finally.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I did arrive to Bochnia on May 3rd, which was three days--",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "September 3rd.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--after my-- September 3rd.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'm sorry.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "September.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I have-- May 3rd is Constitution Day, so it's in my head.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[LAUGHTER] September 1st-- 3rd in the morning, early in the morning.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I walk from the railroad station, which was a very close distance, about 3/4 mile-- kilometers, not mile-- to my home.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And, of course, they were all up already then.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And my mother almost fainted when she saw me, because she just gived up.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "She knew it was 3 and 1/2 kilometers.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The Germans actually made it the same day to Chorzow.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The city itself was not destroyed in 1939.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was no destruction.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But as soon as they came, I found out later that the synagogue in Chorzow-- was a beautiful synagogue in Chorzow-- and that was burned a day after the Germans came.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They did not wait for anything more.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "That synagogue was down in 1939 in September.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not in my home town.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Germans were not in my home town.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- but we knew that the front line is very close.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I knew.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My uncles knew.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My mother knew.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
